			   <div class="topic">AUTUMN Virtual Magnetic Observatory (<a href="http://autumn.athabascau.ca/">http://autumn.athabascau.ca/</a>)</div>
			   <div class="indent">
				  Provides access to data from the Athabasca University Geophysical Observatory (AUGO).
			   </div>
			   
			   <div class="topic">Canadian Space Science Data Portal (CSSDP) (<a href="https://cssdp.ca/">https://cssdp.ca/</a>)</div>
